      <title><![CDATA[Samba]]></title>
      <url>http://jarsonfang.github.io/etesting/2016/09/20/samba/</url>
      <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h2 id="On-Centos"><a href="#On-Centos" class="headerlink" title="On Centos"></a>On Centos</h2><h3 id="安装应用"><a href="#安装应用" class="headerlink" title="安装应用"></a>安装应用</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">yum install samba</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="在home目录下新建samba文件夹"><a href="#在home目录下新建samba文件夹" class="headerlink" title="在home目录下新建samba文件夹"></a>在home目录下新建samba文件夹</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /home &amp;&amp; sudo mkdir samba</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="修改配置文件-etc-samba-smb-conf"><a href="#修改配置文件-etc-samba-smb-conf" class="headerlink" title="修改配置文件/etc/samba/smb.conf"></a>修改配置文件/etc/samba/smb.conf</h3><p>添加如下配置项<br><figure class="highlight plain"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div><div class="line">3</div><div class="line">4</div><div class="line">5</div><div class="line">6</div><div class="line">7</div><div class="line">8</div><div class="line">9</div><div class="line">10</div><div class="line">11</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">[share]</div><div class="line">   comment = shared area</div><div class="line">   public = yes</div><div class="line">   writable = yes</div><div class="line">   path = /home/samba</div><div class="line">   create mask = 0777</div><div class="line">   directory mask = 0777</div><div class="line">   force user = smb</div><div class="line">   force group = smb</div><div class="line">   available = yes</div><div class="line">   browseable = yes</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure></p>
<h3 id="新建用户smb"><a href="#新建用户smb" class="headerlink" title="新建用户smb"></a>新建用户smb</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">adduser smb --shell /bin/bash</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="给新用户设置密码"><a href="#给新用户设置密码" class="headerlink" title="给新用户设置密码"></a>给新用户设置密码</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">passwd smb</div><div class="line">smbpasswd <span class="_">-a</span> smb</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="关闭防火墙"><a href="#关闭防火墙" class="headerlink" title="关闭防火墙"></a>关闭防火墙</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">systemctl stop firewalld.service</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="重启smb服务"><a href="#重启smb服务" class="headerlink" title="重启smb服务"></a>重启smb服务</h3><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">systemctl restart nmb.service smb.service</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h3 id="测试验证"><a href="#测试验证" class="headerlink" title="测试验证"></a>测试验证</h3><p><strong>在/home/samba目录下新建一个测试文件</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div><div class="line">2</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span> /home/samba</div><div class="line">sudo touch readme.txt</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>查看当前板子的IP地址</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><div class="line">1</div></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><div class="line">ip addr</div></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<p><strong>访问samba目录</strong></p>
<p>在PC机上输入：<code>smb://192.168.1.xxx</code><br>在出现的登录界面输入新添加的用户名和密码进行登录</p>
